    <div class="group"><div class="rounded-4xl overflow-hidden aspect-[3/4]"><img class="zoomimg w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487412720507-e7ab37603c6f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt=""></div><div class="mt-3 font-medium">Elena Marchetti</div><div class="text-[13px] text-white/45">Negotiation Coach</div></div>
